Clean orange citrus notes sail across the palate and dovetail with fluffy wheat and our Hazy yeast strain for a smooth mouthfeel. A soft but dry and tangy finish pushes the slurp factor into hyperdrive... As for the name? An all Aussie hopped beer needed an all Aussie beer name.
